#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you already know your way around your operating system, you probably also "
"know how to start &amarok;, and you can <link linkend=\"first-time"
"\">continue</link>. Else, continue reading."
msgstr ""
"Si vous connaissez un peu votre système d'exploitation, vous savez "
"probablement comment lancer &amarok; et vous pouvez <link linkend=\"first-"
"time\">continuer</link>. Sinon, poursuivez la lecture."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "From Plasma"
msgstr "Depuis Plasma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are running the <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:"
"mylanguage/Plasma\">Plasma Workspace</ulink>, you can start &amarok; by "
"either:"
msgstr ""
"Si vous êtes sous <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:mylanguage/"
"Plasma\">l'espace de bureau Plasma</ulink>, vous pouvez lancer &amarok; en : "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"pressing on <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:mylanguage/Kickoff"
"\">Kickoff</ulink> and then <menuchoice><guimenu>Multimedia</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Amarok</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"appuyant sur le menu <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:mylanguage/"
"Kickoff\">Kickoff</ulink> puis <menuchoice><guimenu>Multimédia</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Amarok</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"invoking <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:mylanguage/KRunner"
"\">KRunner</ulink> (<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> by "
"default), entering <varname>amarok</varname> and then pressing &Enter;."
msgstr ""
"appelant <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:mylanguage/KRunner"
"\">KRunner</ulink> (<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> par "
"défaut), puis saisissez <varname>amarok</varname>, appuyez enfin sur &Enter;."

